{
  "stem": "16930.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, all his movies are big.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He didn't have to do this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he did this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He wanted to, because his own-- his also personal development, what he is, what he has become as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and-- and-- and also we see all these movements now of counterculture, which are saying, there was-- the Jews are making it all up.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were no concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe there were a couple hundred Jews killed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some were by accident.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there were no concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What? 6 million Jews got killed?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's impossible.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It could never happen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's all lies.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this counterculture is not only among low-class people, it's been going around universities.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some people even, respectable or-- or officially respectable people, of course they're swine, Nazi swine at heart.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they cannot admit what this kind of-- that would-- and some are Christo-Nazis, Christians who want to destroy the Jewish religion.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when the Jews don't go along, they prepare to the Jews, destroy the Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that whole Nazi culture is based upon Christo-Nazism.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where they have all this-- there's all this ideology against Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's what Hitler was able to work on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Although he himself went to a-- went to a Catholic high school, from which he never graduated.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that's where he got all these ideas of the Jewish being the anti-god, the Christ killers, and the anti-god.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's where he got his all his ideas from regarding Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In the town where he lived, he didn't know any Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There only a few town-- there were only a few Jews in the town where he lived.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were assimilated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He never saw a Jew with a-- with a beard and payot.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
